EASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "945785683870076"}]}, "change_log": "Updates:  Quest v0.1.28 (122) and windows/macOS 0.1.5 (52)\n\nNew Features and updates:\n- You can now apply our materials to your custom assets! \n- Now, it's possible to toggle occlusion on and off per project. \n- New Quest 3 template: A product explorer demo as inspiration on how spatial can enhance e-commerce scenarios. \n- New Quest 3 template: A showcase of all the available triggers.", "created_date": 1728552151, "id": "8350051741699069", "version": "0.1.28", "version_code": 122, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "7189995054371416", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "8352025901501653"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": []}, "change_log": null, "created_date": 1727968209, "id": "8288323874538523", "version": "0.1.27", "version_code": 121, "release_status": "PENDING", "status": "DRAFT", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}, {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "__isAppBinary": "AndroidBinary", "binary_application": {"__typename": "Application", "id": "7189995054371416", "is_concept": false, "latest_released_binary": {"__typename": "AndroidBinary", "id": "8352025901501653"}, "release_status": "RELEASED"}, "binary_release_channels": {"nodes": [{"channel_name": "LIVE", "id": "945785683870076"}]}, "change_log": "Updates:  Quest v0.1.26 (120) and windows/macOS 0.1.5 (49)\n\nToday's update includes an exciting new feature: the States Board! \nThe States Board shows all States and connections currently active in your flow. Simply zoom out of a State and switch to the board. Or zoom into a the State thumbnail and switch back. It's a fast and easy way to keep track of your story line and flow. \n\nNew Features and updates \n- Major under-the-hood upgrades to support the next wave of incredible tools! \n- Fixed an issue where identical names of objects and triggers would cause the misrepresentation of a state \n- Fixed: On Click simulations leading to non-existing states \n- Fixed: Animations don't properly reset - Fixed: On Click on animated GLBs.", "created_date": 1726151545, "id": "8101264553244457", "version": "0.1.26", "version_code": 120, "release_status": "RELEASED", "status": "APPROVED", "binary_test_results": {"nodes": []}, "obb_binary": null, "asset_files": {"count": 0}, "debug_symbols": {"count": 0}, "__isAppBinaryWithFileAsset": "AndroidBinary"}]}}, "viewer": {"user": null}}}